<template>
  <main-layout :page-title="currentPage">
    <template #mainContent>
      <router-view />
    </template>
  </main-layout>
</template>

<script>
import MainLayout from "./layouts/MainLayout.vue";

export default {
  provide() {
    return {
      setCurrentPage: this.setCurrentPage,
    };
  },
  components: {
    MainLayout,
  },
  data() {
    return {
      currentPage: null,
    };
  },
  methods: {
    setCurrentPage(page) {
      this.currentPage = page;
    },
  },
};
</script>
